title: The Bachelorette Australia 2015: Where does Sam Frost live?
text:
NOT only is The Bachelorette’s Sam Frost surrounded by hunky single suitors, she spends her days contemplating her love life inside a North Sydney luxury pad.
Channel 10 has given its viewers a sneak peek of where the 26-year-old hangs out when the camera turns off.
Living room with quality furniture. That view... the Clifton pad used to film The Bachelorette starring Sam Frost. It turns out Frost doesn’t live too shabby at all.
The heritage-listed Clifton home has expensive furniture with chesterfield-style couches, candelabras and plush carpet.
The heritage-listed Clifton home The heritage-listed Clifton home. There are classic chandeliers, wooden floorboards and a waterfront view of the ocean.
The Hunter’s Hill mansion, which houses the remaining Bach blokes, rents for a whopping $25,000 per week.
